ueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015503, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Praise belongs to You for You made it incumbent upon me to thank You, let me know Your Blessings and provided me with health. O my Master! Please honor me with Your Abundant Gifts as You have said, “If ye are grateful, I will add more (favors) unto you; But if ye show ingratitude, truly My Punishment is terrible indeed.” Your Words and Your Promise are true. O my Master! You said, “But if ye count the favors of Allah, never will ye be able to number them…”. And said, “Call on your Lord with humility and in private…”. And said, “…but call on Him with fear and longing (in your hearts): for the Mercy of Allah is (always) near to those who do good.”", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "قُدْسَكَ الْحَمْدُ لَكَ بِمَا اَوْجَبْتَ عَلَيَّ مِنَ الشُّكْرِ (شُكْرَكَ) وَعَرَّفْتَنِيْ مِنْ نَعْمَاۗئِكَ وَاَلْبَسْتَنِيْ مِنْ عَافِيَتِكَ وَاَفْضَلْتَ عَلَيَّ مِنْ جَزِيْلِ عَطِيَّتِكَ فَاِنَّكَ قُلْتَ سَيِّدِيْ‌ لَئِنْ شَكَرْتُمْ لَاَزِيْدَنَّكُمْ وَلَئِنْ كَفَرْتُمْ اِنَّ عَذَابِي لَشَدِيْدٌ وَقَوْلُكَ صِدْقٌ وَ وَعْدُكَ حَقٌّ وَقُلْتَ سَيِّدِيْ‌ وَاِنْ تَعُدُّوْا نِعْمَتَ اللهِ لَا تُحْصُوْهًا وَقُلْتَ‌ ادْعُوْا رَبَّكُمْ تَضَرُّعًا وَخُفْيَةً وَقُلْتَ‌ ادْعُوْهُ خَوْفًا وَطَمَعًا اِنَّ رَحْمَتَ اللهِ قَرِيْبٌ مِنَ الْمُحْسِنِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGr