cription": null, "English": "O my God! I ask You for a little from the very much, in the midst of my many needs from You, and You since eternity are able to do without them, but for me it is gigantic while it is very simple and easy for You. O my God! Truly, when You Pardon my sins, overlook my mistakes, are lenient to my injustice, cover up my foul actions, show forbearance despite my many transgressions committed willfully or negligently, I am tempted to ask You for what I do not deserve.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اَسْئَلُكَ قَلِيْلًا مِنْ كَثِيْرٍ مَعَ حَاجَةٍ بِيْ اِلَيْهِ عَظِيْمَةٌ وَغِنَاكَ عَنْهُ قَدِيْمٌ وَهُوَ عِنْدِيْ كَثِيْرٌ وَهُوَ عَلَيْكَ سَهْلٌ يَسِيْرٌ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّ عَفْوَكَ عَنْ ذَنْۢبِيْ وَ تَجَاوُزَكَ عَنْ خَطِيْئَتِيْ وَصَفْحَكَ عَنْ ظُلْمِيْ وَسَتْرَكَ عَلٰى قَبِيْحِ عَمَلِيْ وَحِلْمَكَ عَنْ كَبِيْرٍ جُرْمِيْ عِنْدَ مَا كَانَ مِنْ خَطَئِيْ وَعَمْدِيْ اَطْمَعَنِيْ فِيْ اَنْ اَسْئَلَكَ مَا لَا اَسْتَوْجِبُهٗ مِنْكَ فَصِرْتُ اَدْعُوْكَ آمِنًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015505, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I persist in calling out, believing in You, and I invoke You, talking familiarly, not afraid, or fearful, but assured of You whenever I turn to You. However, even if there is a short delay, I blame You out of my ignorance, perhaps the delay may be a blessing in disguise because You alone know all the consequences.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَاَسْئَلُكَ مُسْتَانِسًا لَا خَاۗئِفًا وَلَا وَجِلًا مُدِلًّا عَلَيْكَ فِيْمَا قَصَدْتُ فِيْهِ اِلَيْكَ فَاِنْ اَبْطَا عَنِّيْ عَتَبْتُ بِجَهْلِيْ عَلَيْكَ وَلَعَلَّ الَّذِيْ اَ